# Penguin Trailers Inc — Layout Spec

Section-by-section layout for each page. Ordered top-to-bottom as they appear on the page.

**Design rhythm:** Alternate between light (#F3F4F6) and white (#FFFFFF) section backgrounds to create visual separation. Use the dark navy (#003366) sparingly for high-impact CTA sections.

-----

## Home page

|#|Section Type      |Variant                                                                   |Width     |Design Notes                                                                                                                                                        |
|-|------------------|--------------------------------------------------------------------------|----------|--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|
|1|Hero              |Full-bleed image/video with dark overlay. Centered text. Dual CTA buttons.|Full-bleed|Drone yard shot or looping video background. “Since 2006” badge top-left or integrated into headline. Height: 85-100vh. Mobile: stack CTAs vertically.              |
|2|Stats Bar         |Horizontal 4-column number strip                                          |Contained |Navy background, white text. Number + label per stat. Animate numbers on scroll.                                                                                    |
|3|Services Grid     |3-4 column card grid with images                                          |Contained |White background. Cards: image top, title, 2-line description, text link. Hover: subtle lift shadow. Mobile: 2-col or stack.                                        |
|4|Featured Inventory|3-4 column product card grid                                              |Contained |Light grey background. Cards: photo top, type badge, title, key spec, CTA button. Dynamically populated from inventory data. “View All Inventory” button below grid.|
|5|About Teaser      |Split layout — text left, image right                                     |Contained |White background. Jason’s photo on right, story excerpt on left.                                                                                                    |
|6|Image Strip       |Auto-scrolling horizontal image carousel                                  |Full-bleed|Breadner-style ongoing images. 4-6 photos of operations, yard, trailers. Auto-scroll with pause-on-hover.                                                           |
|7|Testimonials      |Single featured quote or carousel                                         |Contained |Light grey background. Build structure now even if testimonials aren’t ready. Large quote marks, reviewer name, company. Placeholder state needed.                  |
|8|CTA Banner        |Full-width colored band with headline + button                            |Full-bleed|Dark navy (#003366) background, white text. Headline + subline + button + phone number.                                                                             |
|9|Footer            |Multi-column footer                                                       |Full-bleed|Dark navy or near-black background. Logo (reversed), nav links, contact info, LinkedIn icon, yard address. Copyright line.                                          |

